dc_title_s: Geological map of the northern part of Vancouver Island and adjacent coasts; by George M. Dawson.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes 3 insets. Includes lists of "Kwakiool Indian names of places." 1 map: col.; 44 x 81 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Dawson, George Mercer, 1849-1901.,Geological and Natural History Survey of Canada.
